{"tid":409778,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天國團聚】腦癌媽為保胎拒化療 產後母嬰相繼離世","createTime":"2017-09-22T10:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T11:09:16.000Z","uid":47272,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8ae714ecaf32adb95e7c4f1c8720a42a0dba345","tid":409778,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:58:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170922&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57240266\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170922%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57240266&d=CQ6U9pJmG1NypnZ2%2BLCg%2BYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=4e4065b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170922%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57240266&h=0f291d80\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170922&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57240266</a><br />\n美國密歇根州一位患腦癌的孕婦，為保胎兒而放棄化療。她最終如願誕下女兒，但母女先後離世。<br />\n<br />\n37歲的卡麗7月已開始昏迷，她的最後願望是誕下利芙（Life Lynn DeKlyen），家人都表示支持。醫生本月初為卡麗剖腹誕下僅24周大的利芙。卡麗分娩三天後逝世。<br />\n<br />\n卡麗（Carrie DeKlyen）的嫂索妮亞（Sonya Nelson）表示，利芙重567克（1磅4安士），留醫期間健康情況反覆，本周轉差，周三晚在密歇根大學醫院離世。<br />\n<br />\n懷孕期間，卡麗本可接受一項實驗性治療，若成功可延長生命10甚至20年，但一旦接受治療，就要犧牲胎兒。卡麗和丈夫德克利恩（Nick DeKlyen）都是基督徒，不想中止懷孕，所以決定不接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n利芙是卡麗與德克利恩的第六位孩子，他們的孩子最大18歲。<br />\n<br />\n索妮亞對所發生的事「無言以對」，只能說：「或許卡麗需要利芙。知道她可與女兒一起回家，我們感到安慰。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/elkbywjf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Felkbywjf&h=f05e0b7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffc17b599a11da6326d48a4e998e630ee930eb24","tid":409778,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fb6586ea301db8e43eb29a68f911a00eba4844","tid":409778,"uid":55511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:59:41.000Z","msg":"goodbye 基督徒"},{"pid":"d72cd3a6f13d604efad90f35b0f93ecd4651ef09","tid":409778,"uid":187,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:59:47.000Z","msg":"On撚9 命得一條<br />\n救撚左自己先啦耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea94568b280671864d209a0def3ebdf0efc03441","tid":409778,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:01:51.000Z","msg":"上帝既安排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3e62cebda672d52e4b47e5b24fe1b5e691d693","tid":409778,"uid":20390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:02:02.000Z","msg":"講就多十年二十年，但有經驗都知腦癌好難醫"},{"pid":"b706f0dbc0fb2f8c8a337058725c391b2bd46e13","tid":409778,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:04:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On撚9 命得一條<br />\n救撚左自己先啦耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個5個仔女咁就冇左個老母"},{"pid":"a96d4d6ab1655f115931686d0c51b1ba0ec2c5f5","tid":409778,"uid":25838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbetween呢d新聞真係唔好post上黎連登<br />\n而家連登d細路係多到你唔信<br />\n講多兩句又話你口德村又剩"}]}